        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Aframomum sericeum. A. habit and inflorescence, scale bar 5 cm; B, leaf sheath and ligule, scale bar 1 cm; C. detail of leaf sheath ornamentation, scale bar 2 mm; D, leaf, scale bar 5 cm; E, adaxial lamina showing free hypodermal sclerenchyma, scale bar 1 mm; F, abaxial lamina and midrib, scale bar 5 mm; G, detail of internal floral structures, scale bar 4 cm; H, anther, scale bar 5 mm; I, stigma, scale bar 5 mm; J, infructescence, scale bar 3 cm. A, G–I from Harris 3266, B–F from Harris 5614, J from Westphal 9754. Drawing by Claire Banks." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894256/files/figure.png" .

